Welcome to Campus Dining
 
At Cal State Fullerton Campus Dining Services, we offer a wide variety of name brand restaurants at multiple locations for your convenience across campus. What makes our locations great is that you can eat where you want, when you want, and exactly what you want for breakfast, lunch, or dinner! No cafeteria food here; we only serve the selections our customers request.







INVEST in csuf
As a nonprofit 501c3 organization, under the division of Cal State Fullerton ASC
, by dining on campus you are investing back into Cal State Fullerton.



Learn More About Investing in CSUF








CSUF Jobs

CalFresh RMP
CalFresh Restaurant Meals Program (RMP) is accepted at our Baja Fresh Express, Togo's, Pieology, Fresh Kitchen, and Carl's Jr. locations.

For more information on how to apply, email basicneeds@fullerton.edu
